"Yesterday noon at the Musashino prison"

19
00:03:03,475 --> 00:03:06,165
-Okay, great! -It's my turn next.

20
00:03:09,475 --> 00:03:12,171
Togashi!

21
00:03:12,171 --> 00:03:15,275
Good work! Great how you hung in there!

22
00:03:15,275 --> 00:03:16,675
Mr. Mouri!

23
00:03:18,775 --> 00:03:22,175
Fumitaka Togashi is a murderer that Pops had arrested

24
00:03:22,175 --> 00:03:23,775
